extendedInfo.description: Jakes Soundboard is sounds and Music from the Hit Kids show Jake and the Neverland Pirates.  It has captain Hook, Jake, scully and all the rest!  Collect your gold deblumes with Jakes crew and his songs!  Your little jake fun will have fun with this app for hours.  For the die hard fans you can even save the sounds and music as ringtones or notifications!  Any problems Please email me!DISCLAIMER: The Pictures associated with this app do not belong to the Disney Corporation.  They were obtained legally through 3rd parties.  The sounds you hear in this app are all publicly available for your listening pleasure on You tube.  We were not the ones to Upload them.  We just Provide a Different way for you to listen to them.   This app is not associated with Disney in anyway.This application complies with US Copyright law guidelines of "fair use". If you feel there is a direct copyright or trademark violation that doesn't follow within the "fair use" guidelines, please contact us directly.
